    <bioghist encodinganalog="MARC 545">
       <head altrender="organization" id="a2">ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY</head>
            <p>The Class Notes are a co-ed a cappella group founded in 1983 that performs a varied repertoire of contemporary Pop, R&amp;B, Rock and Hip-hop songs.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
            <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
                  <p>Music, photos, CDs, videos, sheet music arrangements, membership lists, history and files relating to the administration and performances of the Class Notes.</p>
    </scopecontent>
